             was indicted for <rs id="t18120219-32-off192" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18120219-32-off192" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18120219-32-off192" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18120219-32-cd193" type="crimeDate">24th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120219-32-off192 t18120219-32-cd193"></join>, a watch, value 6 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18120219-32-victim333" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Davidson
                        <interp inst="t18120219-32-victim333" type="surname" value="Davidson"></interp>
